:1},{"word":"race","count":1},{"word":"power","count":1},{"word":"wish","count":1},{"word":"deadly","count":1},{"word":"bloody","count":1},{"word":"beautiful","count":1},{"word":"waltz","count":1},{"word":"overwhelmed","count":1},{"word":"cough","count":1},{"word":"worried","count":1},{"word":"blushing","count":1},{"word":"considerate","count":1},{"word":"darling","count":1},{"word":"besides","count":1},{"word":"cause","count":1},{"word":"any","count":1},{"word":"major","count":1},{"word":"damage","count":1},{"word":"edge","count":1},{"word":"overclock","count":1},{"word":"happen","count":1},{"word":"accept","count":1},{"word":"symptoms","count":1},{"word":"appear","count":1},{"word":"cured","count":1},{"word":"competing","count":1},{"word":"taking","count":1},{"word":"discords","count":1},{"word":"die","count":1},{"word":"field","count":1},{"word":"generated","count":1},{"word":"ignored","count":1},{"word":"anything","count":1},{"word":"interest","count":1},{"word":"regrets","count":1},{"word":"carpe","count":1},{"word":"diem","count":1},{"word":"future","count":1},{"word":"stack","count":1},{"word":"damaged","count":1},{"word":"locate","count":1},{"word":"stellar","count":1},{"word":"three","count":1},{"word":"four","count":1},{"word":"items","count":1},{"word":"tops","count":1},{"word":"remaining","count":1},{"word":"belongs","count":1},{"word":"blake","count":1},{"word":"blooms","count":1},{"word":"represent","count":1},{"word":"bearer's","count":1},{"word":"identity","count":1},{"word":"track","count":1},{"word":"flora's","count":1},{"word":"activity","count":1},{"word":"vanished","count":1},{"word":"appearing","count":1},{"word":"remembered","count":1},{"word":"earlier","count":1},{"word":"saw","count":1},{"word":"seen","count":1},{"word":"somewhere","count":1},{"word":"beatrice","count":1},{"word":"ready","count":1},{"word":"stay","count":1},{"word":"focused","count":1},{"word":"eyes","count":1},{"word":"made","count":1},{"word":"others","count":1},{"word":"tangible","count":1},{"word":"keepsake","count":1},{"word":"frozen","count":1},{"word":"small","count":1},{"word":"task","count":1},{"word":"cake","count":1},{"word":"looks","count":1},{"word":"wanna","count":1},{"word":"copy","count":1},{"word":"excellent","count":1},{"word":"composition","count":1},{"word":"photographer","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"My name is Camellya.","quest_name":"Rewinding Raindrops","quest_id":114000020},{"text":"Try not to let me catch you so easily next time~!","quest_name":"Rewinding Raindrops","quest_id":114000020},{"text":"Hmm... Where is {Male=he;Female=she} hiding?","quest_name":"Rewinding Raindrops","quest_id":114000020},{"text":"Ooh, here you are.","quest_name":"Rewinding Raindrops","quest_id":114000020},{"text":"Aha, you're finally here.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"It's been a while, my sweet <i>seed of fate</i>.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Are you here for the flowers? Perfect timing. They're about to bloom.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Consultants roam all across Solaris, and when they return, they always bring rare flower seeds as souvenirs.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Nah-uh, I just enjoy planting them.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Watching them grow, waiting for them to bloom—you know, waiting makes the fruits so much sweeter.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Of course, I have my own special seed.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Every day, I'm consumed by the urge to see it thrive, trembling with excitement for its bloom, the soft touch of petals unfolding in my palm... This feeling… I can't wait to make it mine!","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Hehe, it's the best thing ever to watch and protect it as its breeder.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Just a little fun of mine. Well, how's it going, {PlayerName}? Enjoying your time here?","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"I heard you got the Shorekeeper and all of us out of a huge mess, huh?","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Hehe, I expected as much. You've shown great potential since you arrived in Jinzhou.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Well... I'm a Bloom Bearer, and a Bloom Bearer knows what they want to know.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Aww, you're a sharp one. Yes, I had something else going on, couldn't say hi to you first. What a pity.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Didn't know the Shorekeeper would entrust a newcomer with such important tasks... She trusts you. A lot.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"You are…","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"\"Oh, congratulations, {Male=Mr.;Female=Ms.} Popularity!\" Whatever…","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"If only you could be mine… I'd root you in my garden, where only I could savor your sweet, robust vitality… Hehe, just kidding. Hope you don't mind.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"…How strange.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"I've felt this way before…","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Hehe, interesting.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"You looking for me?","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Hehe, if you want it, try to catch me!","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Oh, you're quick! I knew you wouldn't keep me waiting.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Yeah, is that a problem?","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"I followed you to the cell on a whim. Then I heard something interesting.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Plus, this thing is just finding its way back to its owner. I see no wrong in that.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Yes and no.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Just like you, I've completely forgotten about the past! All of it! So, I guess I'm not the Lady Flora you're looking for.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Of course, I did some digging, but… a little accident stopped me.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"{PlayerName}, if you want to use that trinket to find the problematic matrix, then play with me! Entertain me, and I'll help you.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Well… Then I'll take this and make a run for it!","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"You can try to catch me, but be warned, it won't be an easy chase. Or, you could play along and maybe I'll let you have it. It'll be more fun that way!","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Since you handled the Threnodian, a little game of battle shouldn't be too much trouble for you, right?","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"As a Bloom Bearer, I need to pick the perfect seeds for the Black Shores and give them my utmost care.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"All these years, I haven't met anyone intriguing—not one person!","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"You're MY seed of fate. If I let you go so easily, all my efforts, my yearning, my hunger will not be satisfied.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"If you get taken or killed by somebody else...","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"...I would be very, very, very unhappy.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Why? It's pure instinct!","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Flowers thirst for water; beasts hunger for flesh. It's nature, just like my craving for you.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"I want it, and I get it. That's how I live.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"So? I don't care! If this island's gonna blow up, so be it. Unless, of course, it ruins my fun.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Are you angry? Hehe, your anger is sooo delicious…","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Fight me. I can't wait to see who'll be the winner. I've been itching to get a taste of your blade.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Hahahaha! Fantastic! Let's get started!","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"What a show. You never disappoint me. With you around, the days ahead will be so much fun.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"The game's over. Here you go, the thing I promised you. Let's keep going, my hero~","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Hehe, alright. So...?","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Haha! Guess I have no other choice, huh?","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"...Well, it's lovely to see you being a little pushy too! I like your serious side. Sure, I'll go.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Yeah, ended up stuck in a boring medical pod for half a month and almost died from severe Overclocking.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Sure, it's no big deal, since I survived.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Hmm... My memories were sealed by Lady Flora somehow. No matter how much I try to recall, it doesn't work.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"I only remember waking up in a cave, my mind completely blank. Drifted aimlessly for years, until I stumbled upon the Black Shores.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"And guess what? Turns out I had lived here before! Naturally, I wanted to investigate further and figure it out.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"So that's what I did. I'm sure I uncovered the truth behind my memory loss, but… when I woke up in the medical pod again, I'd forgotten everything.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Guess somehow I almost died from Overclocking when I learned about my past, and I had to seal my memories away again. That's pretty much what happened, I think?","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"I still don't know why Lady Flora did that though... Well, I don't really care. I can have fun with or without those memories.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Hello~? Are you listening? Told you I remember nothing, so... Lady Flora is more like a stranger to me.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"It's like watching a movie. No matter how happy or sad the story is, it's someone else's story, after all.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Don't you feel the same? Tell me, what was on your mind when you witnessed those stories, staring at every frame on the screen?","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Haha, you don't care, do you? I knew we think alike.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Aww... You are more sentimental than I expected.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Anyway, I'll trust my instincts over some distant memories.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"As long as my instincts remain, I'm still \"me.\"","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Yeah, and what's wrong with that?","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"That's right!","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"My instincts rule me, and I rule them. I feel great joy when they are fulfilled, and when I ignore them, I suffer in return.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"They guide me like how duty and responsiblity guides you... Who says one is better than the other?","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Hehe, let's drop this boring discussion. Shall we split up to find the other stuff?","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Ooh, then it's a competition—I'm in! Let the search begin!","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"{PlayerName}, do you still have that bracelet?","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Good. You can keep it, so... a piece of me always stays with you.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Since the past between us is a secret now, consider this bracelet our witness.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Hehe, it's an old one. It was… a gift.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Got it for monitoring my Rabelle spectrum, as an Overclocking warning device.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"But I don't really need it anymore. Told you I'll never lose control again.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Except in a special situation like this, in most cases, nothing can even leave a scratch on me.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"I hit jackpot finding the matrix. It was a blast! But that's all in the past now.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"No, I'm quite happy with things as they are right now. No need to risk opening the floodgates and winding up in another medical pod.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Since Lady Flora—the past me—chose to seal away those memories, I'm fully behind <i>my</i> decision.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"As for the memories we used to share, if fate decides to reveal them, they'll resurface naturally as we continue our journey together.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Plus… does it really matter? No, it doesn't!","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Fate has already brought us back together.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"I bet we'll have more wild stories to share, and more games to play.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"No point dwelling on the past. I'd rather live in the moment.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"…Speaking of which, I have a question for you.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"{PlayerName}… Are you happy now? Having lost all memories, living a new life...","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Is that so? Good to know. I'm happy too. Every moment <ano=Sparring>dancing</ano> with you brings me immense joy!","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Then... If one day you get tired of all this saving-the-world stuff, I'll whisk you away to a place where no one can find us!","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Heh, same here. But you'll be fine, because you have me now. We can take our time figuring out this life, together!","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"This is where I first set foot on this island, where everything began. The stars lie beneath our feet, where the Tethys System resides.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Tethys records all data on Solaris, capturing countless possibilities born and fading away.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"But in every possible scenario, we always find each other.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"All paths in the stars converge towards this single endpoint, so—","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"The universes where we didn't meet must have all perished! Only this one survived!","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"If the universe were a flower, then yes…","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"...This must be the perfect world for a gardener like me.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Ah... Wonderful…","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"The way you fought really makes my heart race… Such power, such vitality…","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Ugh, I wish I were the one dancing this deadly, bloody, beautiful waltz with you…","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Hehe, I know. I was just overwhelmed with joy… Cough! Ugh…","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Yeah. Oh, are you worried about me?","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Aww, you're sooo sweet. I'm almost blushing.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"That's not considerate, darling. Besides, with the Tethys System here, I can't really cause any major damage.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"And I'm good at dancing on the edge. I won't let myself Overclock that easily. But if it does happen… I'll just accept it as my fate.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Of course I do. But once severe Overclocking symptoms appear, they can't be cured, can they?","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"And I'm happy!","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"It's been a blast competing and taking down those Tacet Discords with you... That's all I need to have a good time.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"If one day I die from Overclocking, so be it! The Black Shores will make sure there's no Tacet Field generated from me.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"I've always followed my instincts, ignored anything that didn't interest me. No regrets, even if I died now.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Carpe diem, enjoy the moment… Life is boring if you're stuck in the past or consumed by the future.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Anyway, what have you found? I got a stack of damaged photos. To locate that Stellar Matrix, we'll need three or four items tops.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"The remaining frequencies... Yes, it belongs to Lady Flora.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"It's been almost 20 years since the last frequencies were recorded.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Blake Blooms represent a Bloom Bearer's identity. They always have one on them. These frequencies can help us track Lady Flora's last activity.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"She and the leader of Black Shores vanished at the same time, no longer appearing in records.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Oh, right. I just remembered what that strange feeling I had earlier was.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"When I saw you in Jinzhou... It felt as if I'd seen you somewhere else before.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Anyway, have you told Beatrice that we're ready?","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"{PlayerName}, stay focused. Don't take your eyes off me!","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"When I found those photos, I made a decision.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Photos are great for capturing memories. Take some photos of me.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"In the past, others recorded us, but now we'll have to do it ourselves.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Consider it... a tangible keepsake.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"They last longer than our memories. A moment frozen in frame.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"As the Black Shores leader, a small task like this would be a piece of cake for you, I bet?","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Looks good. I wanna keep a copy of this too.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Excellent composition. Quite the photographer, aren't you? Hehe…","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000}]}